value.title: Longevity Germany
value.description:
About Event

​We are excited to launch our first ever Longevity SF event!

The fastest growing longevity community in Europe (Longevity Germany) is now launching in the US. Our kick off event will be an urban hike in Golden Gate Park!
Every step we take is a choice to stay alive, stay curious, and stay connected. Let's get to know each other and hit our steps daily count together!
​
Plan:

​10:30 am: we’ll meet in Golden Gate Park for a community hike through the trails, surrounded by redwoods,
